Actions.Text: AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO HIGHER EDUCATION

Title: Provides for the licensure of dietitians and nutritionists; repealer
Summary: Provides for the licensure of dietitians and nutritionists; defines the practice thereof.
LawCode: Rpld §§8004, 8005 & 8006, amd Ed L, generally; amd §§413 & 488, Soc Serv L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law and the social services law, in relation to the licensure of dietitians and nutritionists; and to repeal certain provisions of the education law relating thereto
